profile:
Quality service is something we take very seriously at Goldstone Properties. We believe that providing an excellent quality of service not only creates excellent lawns and properties but also creates excellent relationships between us and our customers. Our customers always come first and we will always treat you like family.

We offer superior year round property services for Winnipeg communities. Our services range from weekly & bi-weekly lawn care, eavestrough cleaning, Spring & Fall cleanups, snow removal and much more. See our Services on this website to browse and contact us through our easy to use contact form to request a free quote. We build Trust with our customers and provide professional services to amazing customers year round.

Contact us today and we will get back to you right away. Goldstone Properties gives quality and customer service you can absolutely count on!
